mie/"], "contributor": ["university of wyoming libraries"], "date": "1911-02-14", "dates": ["1911-02-14"], "description": ["PAGE FOUR SENSATIONAL WINDUP SALE IF YOU DONT WANT TO SAVE MONEY IF YOU SIMPLY WONT BE SHOWN IF YOUD JUST AS LEAVE PAY ANY OLD PRICE FOR YOUR MERCHANDISE WELL NOT EXPECT TO SEE YOU AT THIS SALE IF THE OPPORTU NITY TO SAVE A FEW DOLLARS ON SEASONABLE MERCHANDISE APPEALS TO YOU YOULL BE IN THE CROWD Womens and Childrens Underwear When you have an opportunity like this to lay in a supply of Under wear at WindUp Sale prices it would be an error of judgment not to take advantage of this sale to supply your needs if not for this season for next winter On all vests and pants we are making a reduction of OneThird Womens Coats and Suits We do not want to carry over a single Suit or Coat if we can help it and in order to sell the few rema ning numbers we are making a price on all our Winter Coats and Suits of exactly OneHalf the Regular Price NOTES FROM THE COURT HOUSE I The hall at the court house is being repapered today The treasurers office will be given HtALIil 150 Physicians agree that an improperly purified blood"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-05-31T13:50:11.538Z", "group": ["ndnp/wyu", "university-of-wyoming-libraries"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn92066979/1911-02-14/ed-1/?sp=4", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:wyu:batch_wyu_bradbury_ver01:data:sn92066979:00513687539:1911021401:0970/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=354&w=259", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:wyu:batch_wyu_bradbury_ver01:data:sn92066979:00513687539:1911021401:0970/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=709&w=519", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/wyu/batch_wyu_bradbury_ver01/data/sn92066979/00513687539/1911021401/0970.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["united states", "albany", "albany county", "l